0364d51f9f879b95c6a4a3c9e9fd3d7d1e15ea214c50ae98cd36826b8c0b2d903cf1128741ac83738e305a207dae8955a0b2c8679484d2d6643e334595bdb1d7  our-std-is-good-enough.patch
"
